      "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:48px;\"><strong>為何獵豹特別推薦AMC(下)?</strong></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:22px;\">獵豹數學召集人 宗翰老師撰文</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:22px;\">個人淺見，兩岸三地AMC競賽最專業的教學團隊，首推獵豹數學！！<br />\n<br />\n離2021 AMC10/12已不到兩個月的時間，特地請「獵豹數學召集人」宗翰老師撰文指導，希望能幫助要參加競賽的同學們。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/889037938715559/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/889037938715559/</a></span></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080319074941946-e63f8d6c.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080319074865671-743b8e4c.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080319074981999-82f1616d.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080319074851102-68c63fcd.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080319074988651-8b85bf53.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080319074985509-bf99aad6.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080319074915691-a87f99b3.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080319074933655-aee318a7.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080319075040150-08d540db.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
