      "keep": "保留",
      "targetPage": "columns.html",
      "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<h3 class=\"big-one-two\">化學式要背嗎?</h3>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><br />\n去年深受好評的Sci化學,即將再度開課,熱愛自然科學的孩子們,先來跟耿立老師學習喔!<br />\nSci12國中資優化學<br />\n台大化學碩士 20年升大學教學經驗 耿立老師授課<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/posts/1184525949166755/?__cft__[0]=AZWe8aVun8rwfiNxQV8OarzJEX5X_l18fbzCvzrJ2Z4mlLNlvqc7OfZVn5fj8zoNQfseE57T6LkGvQnFR4BJDt26-RLUw6ghdzr9doxNinLpoz_zFBOoRmB5e9nmazsNPK9MkN8mLytph-PxSAlghjJ9&amp;__tn__=-UK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1184525949166755/</a></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1190573681895315/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1190573681895315/</a></span></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<div class=\"embed-responsive embed-responsive-4by3\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/EOHhfvDASvY?rel=0\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
      "bodyText": "化學式要背嗎?\n\n去年深受好評的Sci化學,即將再度開課,熱愛自然科學的孩子們,先來跟耿立老師學習喔!\n\nSci12國中資優化學\n\n台大化學碩士 20年升大學教學經驗 耿立老師授課\n\n https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1184525949166755/\n\n https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1190573681895315/",
