      "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:28px;\">AMC要的最佳解題方式不僅僅是答對</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><br />\n獵豹的誠聰老師人在上海授課，學生找他討論AMC機率題。<br />\n他藉此比較了強調速度的AMC競賽解題不同的要求與訓練方式。<br />\n我將此文轉貼 供大家參考 。<br />\n明天宗翰老師將會示範許多更精彩的解題方式，大家拭目以待！</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080508161169202-59c040c7.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/r8Y9-3wV0BjObxzFGPf3hQ?fbclid=IwAR2Quh1_z3Yz6w1Isu8oh_R3cx--RJEsnLBFjrLW_neksAqkBL0HuWcRrlo\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/r8Y9-3wV0BjObxzFGPf3hQ?fbclid=IwAR2Quh1_z3Yz6w1Isu8oh_R3cx--RJEsnLBFjrLW_neksAqkBL0HuWcRrlo</a></span></p>\n\n<div class=\"edit\">\n<div class=\"edit\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1116387222647295/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1116387222647295/</a></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
      "bodyText": "AMC要的最佳解題方式不僅僅是答對\n\n獵豹的誠聰老師人在上海授課，學生找他討論AMC機率題。\n\n他藉此比較了強調速度的AMC競賽解題不同的要求與訓練方式。\n\n我將此文轉貼 供大家參考 。\n\n明天宗翰老師將會示範許多更精彩的解題方式，大家拭目以待！\n\n https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/r8Y9-3wV0BjObxzFGPf3hQ?fbclid=IwAR2Quh1_z3Yz6w1Isu8oh_R3cx--RJEsnLBFjrLW_neksAqkBL0HuWcRrlo\n\n https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1116387222647295/",
