      "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:36px;\"><strong>獵豹數學教材的寬廣與前瞻性</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><br />\n本次高雄中學科學班二階口試題「海盜分金」，是獵豹數學國中J和FJ系列的專題教材（在去年獵豹GM家長座談會時,和獵豹網課直播講座中展示過）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>〔獵豹國中數學J71A,J81A+國中競賽FJ71,FJ81 說明及免費公開課〕</strong><br />\n4/17(日) 18:30-20:00 宗翰老師、建廷老師<br />\n將為大家說明國中資優數學的學習安排方式<br />\n以及示範一堂獵豹國中資優數學課!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/posts/1020513472234671/?__cft__[0]=AZX32w4wzGK5l2bsRS18MzGndIUHfKx7WN1VlJnbiySbvtj4t46k0b8ozgIX-oJVUuvPu_aBjwiFjjTzOsjdGkz__7ZdiX5_SaB0xq3NM1QgVChLMZ-DB98rBXvKA-nTMOTxOC_bMG5IxtkbOxgq0Or6&amp;__tn__=-UK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1020513472234671/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1022443458708339/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1022443458708339/</a></span><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081406430634903-7c10d48f.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081406430664537-f912b62c.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081406430638727-39ef2a36.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
      "bodyText": "獵豹數學教材的寬廣與前瞻性\n\n本次高雄中學科學班二階口試題「海盜分金」，是獵豹數學國中J和FJ系列的專題教材（在去年獵豹GM家長座談會時,和獵豹網課直播講座中展示過）。\n\n 〔獵豹國中數學J71A,J81A+國中競賽FJ71,FJ81 說明及免費公開課〕\n\n4/17(日) 18:30-20:00 宗翰老師、建廷老師\n\n將為大家說明國中資優數學的學習安排方式\n\n以及示範一堂獵豹國中資優數學課!\n\n https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1020513472234671/\n\n https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1022443458708339/",
