      "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:36px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:36px;\">獵豹 『北美、上海 國際學校』AMC班課後筆記</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:28px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:26px;\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span></span><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><br />\n明天孩子們就要上AMC8考場了！<br />\n<br />\n星媽特地請獵豹提供孩子們考前衝刺的精華講義，這是獵豹 『北美、上海 國際學校』AMC班級的課後筆記，老師考前叮嚀常見解題原則方法，讓孩子上考場能夠完全發揮實力！<br />\n<br />\n獵豹使用講義電子檔，隨時可以放入最新考題，如美國AMC8/10/12、AIME、USAMO、英國UKMT、加拿大Waterloo CEMC、澳洲AMC。例如這份筆記，老師在課堂中就以2021 UKMT考題為例，讓同學掌握最新考題趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n爸爸媽媽們記得轉給孩子看，明天AMC8考場奪得好成績！<br />\n<br />\n1/23(日)早上獵豹獨家 2022 AMC8獨家解題直播，除了講解考題，還會有延伸補充，歡迎跟星媽報名一起來學習喔!</span><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/posts/967973064155379/?__cft__[0]=AZW4yHVr71IUAM5Ff-rFBYgnB6UEFjauzd2X3c5eqw8EC-BIvOSRQD07tv2Tkb3eYJn-TbznDy9Thg12Wcea1unI_o2v1YObzcjqf0LSuJDYsAHkuoQ823GJtcTyZfSbkYVYpZoU2PicgDmL8qxvcB15&amp;__tn__=-UK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/967973064155379/</a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/969082904044395/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/969082904044395/</a></span></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080506334699318-f9460d9f.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080506334776813-0db904e3.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080506334582088-52d8fd67.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080506334742172-43fe2594.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080506334653833-554433ca.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080506334850579-17602a83.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080506334869458-98b598bb.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080506334721782-6ed918e4.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080506334818015-2df02b47.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080506334875564-cb91e934.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080506334851105-cc5cc3ff.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080506334772516-ff719a52.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080506334865246-592d9964.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080506334876505-eb6fb77e.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
      "bodyText": "獵豹 『北美、上海 國際學校』AMC班課後筆記\n\n明天孩子們就要上AMC8考場了！\n\n星媽特地請獵豹提供孩子們考前衝刺的精華講義，這是獵豹 『北美、上海 國際學校』AMC班級的課後筆記，老師考前叮嚀常見解題原則方法，讓孩子上考場能夠完全發揮實力！\n\n獵豹使用講義電子檔，隨時可以放入最新考題，如美國AMC8/10/12、AIME、USAMO、英國UKMT、加拿大Waterloo CEMC、澳洲AMC。例如這份筆記，老師在課堂中就以2021 UKMT考題為例，讓同學掌握最新考題趨勢。\n\n爸爸媽媽們記得轉給孩子看，明天AMC8考場奪得好成績！\n\n1/23(日)早上獵豹獨家 2022 AMC8獨家解題直播，除了講解考題，還會有延伸補充，歡迎跟星媽報名一起來學習喔!\n\n https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/967973064155379/\n\n https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/969082904044395/",
