      "keep": "保留",
      "targetPage": "columns.html",
      "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<p class=\"big-one-two\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:36px;\">獵豹x未來斑馬</span><span style=\"font-size:22px;\"></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:28px;\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:22px;\"></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:28px;\"><strong>進階Scratch班 公開課</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:22px;\"></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"big-one-two\"><span style=\"font-size:22px;\">炳富老師將利用寒假的Scratch進階課程，帶孩子們運用所學，把自己的想法和創意利用Scratch專案呈現！</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:28px;\"></span></strong></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<div class=\"embed-responsive embed-responsive-4by3\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/lEWCADdhz38?rel=0\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span>孩子們將學到：<br />\n程式的基本概念：序列、條件式、迴圈、變數、運算<br />\n如何除錯：有效率有系統的除錯法<br />\n程式的互動性：使用者體驗的融入與設計<br />\n程式設計的技巧：雛形式開發，混合(Remix)式，回饋的收集<br />\n不只有學習寫程式，還要有能力開發既實用又美觀方便的專案！<br />\n1/9免費公開課，孩子們玩得意猶未盡，徵得老師同意，發出回放，大家一起來學習喔！</span></span><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span></span></span><editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\"></editor-squiggler></p>\n<span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">@media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }\n</style>\n</editor-squiggler></span></p>\n\n<div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span></p>\n<span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/965018984450787/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/965018984450787/</a></span>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\">&nbsp;</p>\n<editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">@media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\">&nbsp;</div>\n</editor-squiggler></div>\n<editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">@media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\">&nbsp;</div>\n</editor-squiggler></div>\n</div>",
      "bodyText": "獵豹x未來斑馬\n\n 進階Scratch班 公開課\n\n 炳富老師將利用寒假的Scratch進階課程，帶孩子們運用所學，把自己的想法和創意利用Scratch專案呈現！\n\n 孩子們將學到：\n\n程式的基本概念：序列、條件式、迴圈、變數、運算\n\n如何除錯：有效率有系統的除錯法\n\n程式的互動性：使用者體驗的融入與設計\n\n程式設計的技巧：雛形式開發，混合(Remix)式，回饋的收集\n\n不只有學習寫程式，還要有能力開發既實用又美觀方便的專案！\n\n1/9免費公開課，孩子們玩得意猶未盡，徵得老師同意，發出回放，大家一起來學習喔！\n\n https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/965018984450787/",
