      "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<h3 class=\"big-one-two\">獵豹SCI系列 科學班與數理資優班考題差異化</h3>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:22px;\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><br />\n許多數理資優的國小、國中孩子，目標是考取高中數資班或是科學班，到底數理資優班和科學班的考試，需要學習到什麼程度？考題又是怎麼樣的？<br />\n<br />\n星媽邀請獵豹X鎮麟Sci宗嶽主任一起來和我們細說。</span></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<div class=\"embed-responsive embed-responsive-4by3\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XJ2JdsatOl4?rel=0\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Sci102針對考數資班/科學班必需的自然科學，在中學物理上給予初學的孩子最好的基礎打底，早鳥即將結束，歡迎想要認真超修，願意挑戰自己的6~8年級孩子，加入Sci學習的行列！</span><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span></span></span><editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\"></editor-squiggler></p>\n<span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">@media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }\n</style>\n</editor-squiggler></span></p>\n\n<div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/940351463584206/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/940351463584206/</a></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\">&nbsp;</p>\n<editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">@media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\">&nbsp;</div>\n</editor-squiggler></div>\n<editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">@media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\">&nbsp;</div>\n</editor-squiggler></div>\n</div>",
      "bodyText": "獵豹SCI系列 科學班與數理資優班考題差異化\n\n許多數理資優的國小、國中孩子，目標是考取高中數資班或是科學班，到底數理資優班和科學班的考試，需要學習到什麼程度？考題又是怎麼樣的？\n\n星媽邀請獵豹X鎮麟Sci宗嶽主任一起來和我們細說。\n\n Sci102針對考數資班/科學班必需的自然科學，在中學物理上給予初學的孩子最好的基礎打底，早鳥即將結束，歡迎想要認真超修，願意挑戰自己的6~8年級孩子，加入Sci學習的行列！\n\n https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/940351463584206/",
