      "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<h3 class=\"big-one-two\">如何學好化學(下)-耿立老師</h3>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">昨天耿立老師文中和大家分享如何學好化學，其中一個學習的秘密就是「以圖通理」，化學式怎麼記？<br />\n<br />\n今天耿立老師特地為星媽獵豹社團的孩子們錄一段教學，爸爸媽媽們一定要讓孩子來看喔！</span><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/908961143389905/\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/908961143389905/</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<div class=\"embed-responsive embed-responsive-4by3\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/EOHhfvDASvY?rel=0\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
