      "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:36px;\">學習的路上有好的老師引導尤為重要！</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">今天是教師節，星媽特地向獵豹宗翰老師邀稿。<br />\n<br />\n學習的路上有好的老師引導尤為重要！<br />\n<br />\n文中所提著名的Cavendish Laboratory 令人神往：大師的高瞻遠矚，人才薈萃的同儕團體，薪火相傳，培養出一代代優秀的科學家和諾貝爾獎得主！<br />\n<br />\n期待同學也能在獵豹老師的指導、優秀同學的互相砥礪下，激發潛力、邁向成功！<br />\n<br />\n祝福我們最親愛的老師們，教師節快樂！</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/897596884526331/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/897596884526331/</a></span></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023082802322954301-18346462.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023082802322877498-1f5dddf7.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023082802322841985-dc869668.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
