      "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<h3 class=\"big-one-two\"><span style=\"font-size:28px;\"></span>「數學」與「程式」的精彩結合<span style=\"font-size:26px;\"></span><small></small></h3>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">星很喜歡數學中的幾何題，他也在去年的APMO(亞太數奧)一題幾何得到了滿分，我發現他在做幾何題的時候，也常利用Geogebra輔助觀察和思考，後來我看到了 獵豹朱安強老師 的Geogebra作品，才知道，原來Geogebra能做到的比我所知的多更多！<br />\n<br />\n這裡分享一段朱安強老師的Geogebra簡介，看完我都想學了!也推薦給大家！</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><u style=\"color: rgb(0, 158, 145); font-size: 20px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/818075355811818/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/818075355811818/</a></u></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<div class=\"embed-responsive embed-responsive-4by3\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/H7QupZQ0Y-U?rel=0\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
