      "keep": "保留",
      "targetPage": "columns.html",
      "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:28px;\">說說「優雅」</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><br />\n硯吉老師的優雅是「形而上」：觀念的的優雅、觀點的卓越。<br />\n<br />\n我這呼應一下 「形而下」的優雅 ：體力活的減輕，汗水少流些。</span></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112583212630-af580e47.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">前幾年武陵高中科學班入學考 ，考完後一位學生很高興的來找我說：「老師，你猜中一題，讓我秒殺！」<br />\n我：「哦？那道題？」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:20px;\">他拿出計算紙秀了題目（Fig1）<br />\n<br />\n我：「誒？我沒講這題啊！」<br />\n學生：「你前幾天考前講座不是上了這題嗎（Fig2）？ 你是這樣解的！（Fig3）所以我這樣解：（Fig4）」</span></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073113032996010-c76088ad.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<div class=\"edit\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">聰明的孩子！<br />\n<br />\n註：武陵這題是1983.AHSME-P23(Fig5)是一般常規的作法</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/721244105494944/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/721244105494944/</a></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073113032923117-f3d1247b.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112583234850-3493594f.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112583261228-6c1a0db9.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112284760849-f989c8a8.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112284714324-9d314e32.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
      "bodyText": "說說「優雅」\n\n硯吉老師的優雅是「形而上」：觀念的的優雅、觀點的卓越。\n\n我這呼應一下 「形而下」的優雅 ：體力活的減輕，汗水少流些。\n\n 前幾年武陵高中科學班入學考 ，考完後一位學生很高興的來找我說：「老師，你猜中一題，讓我秒殺！」\n\n我：「哦？那道題？」\n\n 他拿出計算紙秀了題目（Fig1）\n\n我：「誒？我沒講這題啊！」\n\n學生：「你前幾天考前講座不是上了這題嗎（Fig2）？ 你是這樣解的！（Fig3）所以我這樣解：（Fig4）」\n\n 聰明的孩子！\n\n註：武陵這題是1983.AHSME-P23(Fig5)是一般常規的作法\n\n https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/721244105494944/",
      "imageUrl": "pic/columns/2023073112583212630.png",
      "notes": "舊站自動搬移於 2026-03-24",
      "migrationPage": "news/cheetah-salon",
      "listDescription": "宗翰老師十年前一篇關於AMC的分析文章，經老師同意，在此和大家分享，希望讓大家對AMC有更深入的了解。",
      "legacyCategoryUrl": "https://www.cheetahstem.com/news/11/1",
      "legacyCategoryId": 11
